lead_paragraph: After the frenzy of the transfer window saw big-name foreign stars land mega-money deals, the Chinese Super League kicked off its new season in an empty stadium as newly-promoted Guizhou Zhicheng were held to a 1-1 draw by 10-man Liaoning Whowin.
